skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: inner genius
des:
The way you collect, process, learn and communicate information is exclusive to you. It's your unique Inner Genius: the filter through which you connect with the world.
Fast-track your next promotion. Unlock your family's learning. Supercharge your team. Connect with your family and friends better. 
Unlock your Inner Genius now.

Learn more at innergeniusnow.com

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Inner Genius" or "Alexa, open Inner Genius" to get a tip.

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
